# font size

- https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/forums/t/743402/how-to-change-font-size-in-grub-menu/

Uncomment **GRUB_GFXMODE=640x480** in `/etc/default/grub`, or choose another supported resolution.

## Find out supported video resolutions

	**grub menu** -> c -> **grub>** -> videoinfo (for grub-efi, vbeinfo for grub-pc)
